<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />早安！<tag a="110" b="4" />。<10_4 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />虽然现在起床是有点早，<delay20 />
但我就是不可思议地醒过来了呀。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />偶尔试试做点和平时不一样的事，<delay20 />
非常有新鲜感，很不错哦。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总感觉内心十分不平静，<delay20 />
于是这么早就醒来了呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />接着我就遇见了你！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />令沉眠之<tag a="110" b="10" />
睁开了双眼的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />或许就是你呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晨安！<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是比平时起得要早一些，<delay20 />
清晨腿抽筋之后，<delay20 />
我就再也未能入眠。<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />或许是某人的思念<delay20 />
将沉眠之<tag a="110" b="10" /><delay20 />
从梦境中唤醒的呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天不知为何，<delay20 />
还丝毫没有倦意呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，在这样安静的时间里，<delay20 />
放松心情坦率面对自己，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感觉也很不错呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦呀，<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
睡不着吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其实我也是<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />深夜的静寂犹如魔法，<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />难免使人错觉
时光永无尽头。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />情绪也随之高涨，<delay20 />
一夜无眠迎来天光<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在刚巧<delay20 />就是这种感觉呢～</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />晚上好！<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="4" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知为何，今夜无法入眠。<10_4 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也和我一样吗？<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果你愿意，我们来聊一聊吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在这属于成年人的时间里<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>